01:22:22.237 --> 01:22:25.115
Honey!
Why the gloom?

01:22:25.507 --> 01:22:27.509
It's not the end
of the rainbow.

01:22:29.210 --> 01:22:31.579
I'm Navin Johnson,
inventor!

01:22:31.579 --> 01:22:34.525
This is no big deal.
It's a parking ticket to me.

01:22:34.983 --> 01:22:37.827
Only instead of $5,
it's $10,000,000.

01:22:39.154 --> 01:22:41.861
I don't care about
losing all the money.

01:22:42.891 --> 01:22:45.234
It's losing all the stuff.

01:22:46.461 --> 01:22:48.565
We're not gonna
lose the stuff.

01:22:48.897 --> 01:22:50.031
[Chuckling]

01:22:50.031 --> 01:22:51.733
This is America!

01:22:51.733 --> 01:22:55.703
We're gonna receive
a fair trial from
an impartial jury.

01:22:56.237 --> 01:22:57.339
[Mallet pounding]

01:22:57.339 --> 01:23:00.513
Your Honor, we, the jury,
find for the plaintiff.

01:23:00.875 --> 01:23:02.217
[People applauding]

01:23:06.181 --> 01:23:08.718
I award, to Mr. Reiner

01:23:09.384 --> 01:23:11.586
and the other nine million

01:23:11.586 --> 01:23:14.255
nine hundred and 87 thousand

01:23:14.255 --> 01:23:16.826
six hundred
and 52 plaintiffs,

01:23:17.525 --> 01:23:19.402
the full amount of the suit.

01:23:21.396 --> 01:23:23.375
Court is adjourned!

01:23:23.732 --> 01:23:25.734
[People applauding]

01:23:29.704 --> 01:23:30.910
Navin.

01:23:31.039 --> 01:23:32.882
Honey, can't you see
I'm drinking?

01:23:39.848 --> 01:23:41.918
Pay to the order of

01:23:43.084 --> 01:23:45.188
Mrs. Wilbur Stark

01:23:46.788 --> 01:23:49.200
$1.09!

01:24:05.840 --> 01:24:07.546
Pay to the order of

01:24:08.810 --> 01:24:11.654
Iron Balls McGinty

01:24:13.248 --> 01:24:15.625
$1.09!

01:24:17.685 --> 01:24:18.953
Why are you crying?

01:24:18.953 --> 01:24:21.156
And why are you
wearing that old dress?

01:24:21.156 --> 01:24:23.324
Because I just heard
a song on the radio

01:24:23.324 --> 01:24:25.394
that reminded me
of the way we were.

01:24:25.727 --> 01:24:27.128
What was it?

01:24:27.128 --> 01:24:28.504
The Way We Were.

01:24:29.097 --> 01:24:31.474
[Sniffling]
Look at us.
We've hit bottom.

01:24:31.766 --> 01:24:35.770
No! Maybe you've hit bottom,
but I haven't hit bottom yet!

01:24:36.337 --> 01:24:38.282
I've got a ways to go!

01:24:39.140 --> 01:24:40.744
And I'm gonna bounce back!

01:24:40.875 --> 01:24:42.285
And when I do,

01:24:42.577 --> 01:24:45.922
I'm gonna buy you
a diamond so big

01:24:46.181 --> 01:24:48.251
it's gonna make you puke.

01:24:49.184 --> 01:24:51.252
I don't wanna puke!

01:24:51.252 --> 01:24:53.026
I don't want wealth!

01:24:53.588 --> 01:24:56.659
I just want you
like you used to be.

01:24:56.991 --> 01:24:58.993
What happened to that man?

01:24:58.993 --> 01:25:00.437
Me?

01:25:00.962 --> 01:25:03.271
What happened to
the girl I believed in?

01:25:04.199 --> 01:25:06.008
The girl I fell in love with.

01:25:06.134 --> 01:25:08.170
The girl that believed in me.

01:25:09.904 --> 01:25:12.273
There's plenty of places
I can go,

01:25:12.273 --> 01:25:14.242
where people
believe in me.

01:25:14.242 --> 01:25:15.577
Well, go!

01:25:15.577 --> 01:25:17.645
The sooner
you're out of my life,

01:25:17.645 --> 01:25:19.848
the sooner I can go back
to being the girl

01:25:19.848 --> 01:25:21.749
in this little flowered dress

01:25:21.749 --> 01:25:25.788
that you sang
the thermos song to.

01:25:26.187 --> 01:25:27.996
Well, I'm gonna go, then!

01:25:29.023 --> 01:25:32.026
And I don't need any of this!
I don't need this stuff!

01:25:32.794 --> 01:25:35.297
And I don't need you!
I don't need anything!

01:25:37.065 --> 01:25:38.202
Except this.

01:25:39.200 --> 01:25:42.010
This ashtray.
The only thing I need is this!

01:25:43.872 --> 01:25:47.182
I don't need this or this.
Just this ashtray!

01:25:48.877 --> 01:25:50.287
And this paddle game.

01:25:51.746 --> 01:25:54.453
The ashtray
and the paddle game.
And that's all I need!

01:25:55.250 --> 01:25:58.419
And this remote control.

01:25:58.419 --> 01:26:00.955
The ashtray, the paddle game,
and the remote control.

01:26:00.955 --> 01:26:02.593
And that's all I need!

01:26:04.959 --> 01:26:06.438
And these matches.

01:26:07.695 --> 01:26:10.098
The ashtray and these matches

01:26:10.098 --> 01:26:12.771
and the remote control
and the paddle ball.

01:26:14.802 --> 01:26:15.939
This lamp.

01:26:18.306 --> 01:26:19.546
The ashtray,

01:26:21.643 --> 01:26:24.453
this paddle game
and the remote control,

01:26:25.813 --> 01:26:27.986
and the lamp.
And that's all I need.

01:26:28.750 --> 01:26:30.024
