Some kind of
a jerk or something?

01:26:56.277 --> 01:26:57.551
[Sobbing]

01:27:02.450 --> 01:27:03.519
And this.

01:27:05.587 --> 01:27:07.088
That's all I need.

01:27:08.223 --> 01:27:09.565
The ashtray,

01:27:10.158 --> 01:27:12.763
the remote control
and this paddle game,

01:27:13.228 --> 01:27:16.231
and this magazine
and the chair.

01:27:16.631 --> 01:27:17.973
[Sobbing]

01:27:22.370 --> 01:27:24.706
And I don't need
one other thing.

01:27:24.706 --> 01:27:26.608
Except my dog.

01:27:26.608 --> 01:27:27.916
[Growling]

01:27:29.410 --> 01:27:30.980
I don't need my dog.

01:28:39.547 --> 01:28:41.890
(Navin)
So, that's it.

01:28:42.917 --> 01:28:44.327
It's an old story.

01:28:44.986 --> 01:28:47.022
One you've probably
heard before.

01:28:47.522 --> 01:28:49.194
[Cars honking]

01:28:49.424 --> 01:28:51.904
But I never thought
it would happen to me.

01:28:54.028 --> 01:28:55.472
[Sighing]

